folder: Corlears Hook - Grand Street., Manhattan, NY
text:
East river, at Carleans Hook, and the foot of Grand Street, showing a new East River Drive park and a fireboat dock. Shown too is the 'Williamsburg Bridge'.

P. L. Sperr
August, 1939
Views 1,2,3
